_sText:
Map by: SixThree - sdunfee@gmail.com
Map name: aim_ag_brickedin
Date created: 30/12/04
Work: 9 hours

About: Two teams hunt eachother down in a maze of wooden crates. The team that controls the bridge 
controls the maze. Take it at all costs. All weapons are enabled, but you'll find that some combinations
work better than others...

TO INSTALL: Place the .bsp (aim_ag_brickedin.bsp) in your 
C:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\your@email.com\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps folder.
